---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import PageHeader from '../../components/PageHeader.astro';
---

<Layout title="Fire Rebuilds In Sonoma County – Annadel Builders Inc." description="Annadel Builders helps Sonoma County families rebuild after wildfire devastation. Expert fire rebuild services.">
  <PageHeader title="Fire Rebuilds In Sonoma County" bgImage="/images/Santa-Rosa-Foothills-Fire-Rebuild-sonoma-3-1-1200x800-1.png" />

  <section class="max-w-[1140px] mx-auto px-4 py-16">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto space-y-6">
      <p>Our team at Annadel Builders, Inc. has helped many families in Sonoma County and surrounding communities rebuild in the wake of wildfire devastation. As dedicated members of our beautiful Northern California community, we are profoundly familiar with wildfire loss and the disruption caused by fire-related displacement. If you are looking to rebuild after a fire, let our team of dedicated Santa Rosa fine home builders help you come home again. Get in touch at <a href="tel:7075796282" class="text-teal hover:underline">(707) 579-6282</a> to arrange a meeting with our team.</p>
      <p>This client's home was destroyed in the 2017 Tubbs Fire. We were honored to spearhead their new rebuild on the same homesite in the Santa Rosa foothills.</p>
      <img src="/images/Santa-Rosa-Foothills-Fire-Rebuild-sonoma-3-1-1200x800-1.png" alt="Santa Rosa fire rebuild by Annadel Builders" class="w-full h-auto mt-8" loading="lazy" />
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
